00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:21.610
Co-founder of numerous progressive nonprofit
organizations.

00:00:21.610 --> 00:00:23.720
A husband and a father.

00:00:23.720 --> 00:00:29.290
And he is here today to talk about Rebuild
the Dream, that platform as outlined in his

00:00:29.290 --> 00:00:31.400
new book.

00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:32.400
Here's the advertisement.

00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:34.520
[Laughter]
&gt;&gt;female speaker: Anyway please welcome, Van

00:00:34.520 --> 00:00:35.960
Jones Johnson.

00:00:35.960 --> 00:00:43.470
[Applause]
&gt;&gt;Van Jones: See you're kind a lopsided on

