00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:51.120
Well first of all I'm glad to be here.

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:55.390
This is the first talk I've given on the book.

00:00:55.390 --> 00:00:57.330
I've been on TV, but it's been really short.

00:00:57.330 --> 00:01:00.660
So I'm gonna get a chance to talk for a little
